Package entities

Class Item

java.lang.Object
entities.Item
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Comparable<Item>
Direct Known Subclasses:
Kevlar, MediKit
public abstract class Item
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<Item>
Represents an abstract item in a game that has a name and a position. The Item class provides functionality to manage its position and implements the Comparable interface to allow comparison based on the item's value.
